@startuml context
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam defaultFontColor #2C3E50
skinparam backgroundColor  #FAFBFC
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 6
skinparam ArrowColor #5D6D7E
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam linetype ortho

title SDI Helper - System Context (C4 L1)
header  Vehicle SDI Platform  |  sdi-helper-architecture  |  ML Platform Team
footer  v1.0  |  Internal

actor "ML Engineer" as User #08427B
note bottom of User: Triggers scrape runs,\nconfigures quotas and queries

rectangle "**SDI Helper**\n//Automated dataset builder//\n--\nScrapes, filters, classifies and\nlabels vehicle images for\nYOLO model training" as System #1168BD

rectangle "Google Images\n<<image source>>"    as Google #F5F5F5
rectangle "Bing Images\n<<image source>>"      as Bing   #F5F5F5
rectangle "DuckDuckGo\n<<image source>>"       as DDG    #F5F5F5
rectangle "OLX / Mobil123\n<<image source>>"   as Used   #F5F5F5
rectangle "AWS S3\n<<dataset store>>"          as S3     #F5F5F5
rectangle "Vehicle SDI Platform\n<<consumer>>" as SDI    #F5F5F5

User   --> System : configures and operates
System --> Google : Selenium / HTTP
System --> Bing   : Selenium / HTTP
System --> DDG    : HTTPS
System --> Used   : HTTP scraping
System --> S3     : s3:PutObject\n(images, labels,\nmanifests, state)
S3     --> SDI    : aws s3 sync\nfor YOLO training

legend right
| **Stereotype** | **Meaning** |
| person         | Human actor |
| system         | System in scope |
| image source   | Upstream image provider |
| dataset store  | Persistent artifact store |
| consumer       | Downstream system |
endlegend
@enduml
